<MELItem itemNbr="34-31-04" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-34-31-04.1.2-34-31-04_FAA">
<Title>VOR Navigation Systems</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="D" nbrInstalled="2" nbrRequired="1">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One may be inoperative provided one GPS is operative.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationNote>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Consider remaining navigation and approach capability in the event of enroute failure of additional integrated navigation radio functions.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>For RNAV 5 or RNAV 1, RNAV 2 operations, one GPS receiver must be operative for FMS navigation update. </Para>
<Note>
<Para>For RNAV 1, RNAV 2 with legs below MSA-without radar coverage - two GPS must be operative.</Para>
</Note>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>For single VOR inoperative, the SGL SOURCE APPROACH caution message may be displayed.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</OperationNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
</DispatchItems>